casebody.data:
STATE of Louisiana
v.
Grover D. CANNON NO. 2019-KK-0531 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 6, 2019

Granted in part, denied in part. This matter is remanded and the district court is ordered to expeditiously conduct an evidentiary hearing on the age-based claims in defendant's motion to quash.

In all other respects, defendant's writ is denied. Defendant's request for a stay of the proceedings is also denied.
